data.description: This 6885 square foot single family home has 6 bedrooms and 5.0 bathrooms. This home is located at 25374 Deep Canyon Dr, Star, ID 83669.
data.whatILove: Enjoy a home built for entertaining right on the edge of Eagle, yet close to all major shopping and cities. A host's dream and child’s play land, this house is sure to leave you and your guests with great memories. Vaulted ceilings and big bay windows will leave you enchanted with the farm views by day and city lights by night. Overlooking Eagle and Bogus Basin is just the beginning. An oversized chef’s kitchen with double islands, fully finished basement with private entrance, full guest quarters, family room and nook in kitchenette area, billiards room, and surround sound movie theater are just some of this home's amazing features. Multiple rooms to make your own practical spaces. Plus heated/cooled 5 car garage and more! The 360 views and estate feel of this home will leave you the talk of the town.
